00:24:57,220 --> 00:25:01,300
So I would request you to ask me questions, few questions,

181
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:05,440
and then if you want, we can have the session of meditation,

182
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:10,260
in which you can feel your all-pervading power.

183
00:25:23,020 --> 00:25:28,060
