239
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:50,240
and anybody who takes money from you

240
00:33:50,420 --> 00:33:53,560
is a false master.

241
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:09,220
And you cannot pay for it.

242
00:34:10,540 --> 00:34:14,040
Or it is also not outside, like you go on chanting

243
00:34:14,220 --> 00:34:17,300
or saying something.

244
00:34:20,520 --> 00:34:23,800
It's a happening within.

